This a Full Remote job, the offer is available from: Portugal, Spain

"

We are Plexus.Tech, a technology company specializing in IT services and products, founded on the talent and capabilities of our people, more than 2,800 professionals developing technology products and services that make life better for people, companies and institutions. Based on a model of closeness, speed and flexibility.

Among our main international clients, we have practically all of the IBEX35 companies stand out, as well as large retailers, tour operators, airline companies and financial entities.

We are increasing our Talents team! Do you dare to continue training in cutting-edge technologies on the market? Then you must join the Plexus.Tech family. If you want to progress and face new challenges, this is your opportunity.

REACT DEVELOPER - Remote (Portugal or Spain)

Join us if you have:
• +2 years of experience with React
• Experience with hooks
• Experience with TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML/CSS
• Testing Experience
• Fluent english & Fluent portuguese
• Working in Agile environment (Scrum experience)

If you are worried about continuing your progression, this is your time!!!!!

You will be part of a team of more than 2,800 professionals and increase your professional projection with us.

WHAT WE OFFER:
• Integration into one of the largest ecommerce platforms in the world
• Permanent contract + 100% remote
• Flexible compensation package
• Health insurance
• "Flexology"*
• Professional projection inserted in a team of 2800 professionals
• Access to ongoing training
• Be part of a dynamic team, committed, passionate about its customers and willing to give the best of themselves
• Be part of a company with many leading professionals in the sector
• A work ecosystem with a collaborative environment

FLEXOLOGY: we are an adaptable, flexible and hybrid company. We are committed to a model based on putting people, our people, who are the pillar of our company, at the centre. We care about your talent, your skills and, above all, your well-being. Therefore, we adapt to new situations and demands so that people flow professionally and personally. A model based on trust.

In this way, Plexus.Tech professionals do their work and develop their talent where they work best, being able to choose to work from home or in any of our 24 offices, combining the best of both options.

We are passionate about technology, but above all we love the people who make it possible. Because with motivation, enthusiasm and teamwork we are doing fantastic things.

"This offer from "Plexus Tech" has been enriched by Jobgether and got a 78.25% flex score.
